This is a production-grade full-stack application.

Frontend:
- Next.js App Router
- React
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS

Backend:
- Express.js
- Prisma ORM
- PostgreSQL

Rules:
- Do not rewrite working modules.
- Preserve existing architecture.
- Reuse existing components before creating new ones.
- Follow the current folder structure.
- Maintain role-based access (ADMIN, EDITOR, CLIENT).
- Never break existing APIs.
- Prefer small, focused edits over large refactors.
- Keep TypeScript strict with no type errors.
- Follow enterprise-level UI consistency.